looks like it might not be. I'm wondering if I could use `sun.misc.Unsafe.defineClass` to define `sun.misc.BASE64Encoder` into the app loader. But has it been removed? It seems like I should look into the build native-image properties to see if they might allow this. Let's do some digging!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0e79fc3ea7b47e140169eff7d04f4081948fcd786eac031f41\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp7_fkIVXu7loHiAWKUiP7qU0LB8Sp4piBTngXK7XSBwFHXroXN0an7BMLsVIpHVHH6WVkx0sUojQII_H1ows30hKpNYoWq-mXKCUzfdxXQmOkjuzh4L142O_AH3EfkpAykoaPONiAZrMriZW8D_rQRDRCX9H_REh0YruC_9B_weM6TYQvj_QHTVPjd4Hr1w6fMreStlJv31nc8d4VBZSLupow9zRGP5qp0xkbRIIab6K6QMmlr6rW0r-bxsPX3HBOgdwJpmur69OBGK9Oklpw6fsr0V9wzAHSYKjb9OL5aP-SX6scAAs-IW_9hsd7KXPIIOmavLQ_3GbLKODv0e_pXV0XKk6rVauCuQeW7pnfzBYpXKoIFcnMQ__czwkCdHEl0-8uIPtBrJKRQ6hWDbL4AI9r9DG0dtsrlkC84tVEybqZm-amXGxrTvIfMMsnb8HYciDpCoFNsEWaPz03Db1Xef77DTjzWe7xyAkkav9UZNA3Hrq0MVkriiBKNY68Xcev8Jb_ryrYuhoV7KrAVX4te6nC2zarWZ3IDUrw_r4tq56Hz6uv8SIczNqupMa_BjyJ9R7Z0lOkUnQLWnx0kPvWnvByvLCo8W-CN7EHK2yzgxUIRAZ2bov-XdOtOL6AxJ0li1IEu1MSK0aUGVmAZnWG5hCCrzyUDIqzdk4sAzs-S0WgRm6A5qT3iIZm2wACyn4g0EqmrkEEZsGioc-KORlA5hqA2t3g0qz7v6olHYwANkMhX4xAt6RiNklMoEkxc1ZJGcPG3hrGHlQHcQGgWsjQT8FrEWWf-B4dnZYM1rpQxIMsPY2CIKKIOH_JwVietGKHOmDV12gyZtXM_x7bOtr4jTR74A6B5XQwH8toL9FkxCtR3WWd3V8EU2coNfGnhi7CIXPiohrTnkkvx9xQa-Yx3T-Pbpm0bMhgmb3EkWDeTv9h4eunxGkOve7dbGYuwn6Ioeffnp3gzWv-0su4B8GP37jgQMnsWIM5ejITOt55t7_twheOgkBiOGvBB0tojCJ3iV9Kp6PKdIYaRbjF3QrEU4esFKTppEpzareb_uuseOKI2wimC3FulCHmDzdhbNVGUwNAteAFo8H81sNKa8ggUg6MlMj8u_W7oZd1_iKRZbebS7Y_CYeCLMgXj9uR_tk2ouvHNcAo-DwisOWKAOdwmo1Ti63Xgs98Zg0qp4F4ALwOvMQyXyvtCYFjCdwIBLflPT9XN_pZmyP7BZFq9yuSgsrpbfKI0AwYSaU2hyot8yumJY2NQ7xHxJ7xy_2E3Jz7JXRf6XV9KQXbQDCfkR8KCcmmdx9aT4881IrQbWFKxuUnhqOiVJGthZZ7XOY1YAMAsWFzwT3lrjLdQTGE3DALJb7oQSlknM9C-NbXs_UaxlEFp4jJ6XCxptxAHdU9PvYdxAxWKhVtg1qdi9NBUJyt41EVDYCFcncKH2QVrn1tzn-I6MmAacym5ZOkxa3TH553Fz1jMOGPDgFw8mhLg1eg9OQIvz1Riy7S9JPRhuZajaNTj-7w2vdNRkovRHlu7yzmisG_CgXcm2EYYfKoyA6WoRhxy6sM